ezvcard.io
Class HCardPage

java.lang.Object
  ezvcard.io.HCardPage

public class HCardPage
extends Object

Writes VCard objects to a templated HTML page (hCard format).

Example: 

 VCard vcard1 = ...
 VCard vcard2 = ...
 
 HCardPage page = new HCardPage();
 page.add(vcard1);
 page.add(vcard2);
 
 File file = new File("hcard.html");
 page.write(file);

Author:
Michael Angstadt
See Also:
http://microformats.org/wiki/hcard
